title: Teen Angel
overview: Teen Angel is an American teen fantasy serial drama series that aired on the Disney Channel. Starring Jason Priestley. The series was first broadcast on The All New Mickey Mouse Club (MMC) on April 24, 1989. Ended its run on May 22, 1989. Teen Angel was followed by a sequel series, Teen Angel Returns, also starring Priestley and Jennie Garth, which aired from October 2 to October 27, 1989.
